OL,3,CIran-US deal ignores what Iranian
OL,4,Cpeople want, son of last Shah tells
OL,5,CITV News
OL,7,FThe son of the last Shah, Reza
OL,8,FPahlavi, sat down with ITV News'
OL,9,FGlobal Security Editor to discuss the
OL,10,Fagreement between Iran and the US.
OL,12,FIran's preliminary peace agreement
OL,13,Fwith the United States ignores what
OL,14,Fthe Iranian people want, exiled crown
OL,15,Fprince Reza Pahlavi has told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781722095
OL,3,CIran-US deal ignores what Iranian
OL,4,Cpeople want, son of last Shah tells
OL,5,CITV News
OL,7,F"40,000 Iranians haven't died in the
OL,8,Fspan of two days for a nuclear deal or
OL,9,Ffor the Strait of Hormuz to remain
OL,10,Fopen", Pahlavi exclaimed as he
OL,11,Fconsidered whether the impending
OL,12,Fsigning of a preliminary peace deal
OL,13,Fwas a positive development for the
OL,14,Fpeople of Iran.
OL,16,FHe told ITV News: "They have died for
OL,17,Fthe sake of liberty, and freedom, and
OL,18,Fdemocracy. And they've been oddly
OL,19,Fabsent in any negotiations."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
