OL,3,CIran-US deal ignores what Iranian
OL,4,Cpeople want, son of last Shah tells
OL,5,CITV News
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe son of Iran's last Shah, Reza
OL,13,FPahlavi, has lived in exile in America
OL,14,Fsince his father was ousted in the
OL,15,Frevolution of 1979.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781722095
OL,3,CIran-US deal ignores what Iranian
OL,4,Cpeople want, son of last Shah tells
OL,5,CITV News
OL,7,FThe figure of 40,000 he referred to
OL,8,Fwas the purported death toll that
OL,9,Ffollowed the Iranian government's
OL,10,Fviolent repression of protests that
OL,11,Fhad built during the early weeks of
OL,12,Fthis year.
OL,14,F"As they are talking about
OL,15,Fnegotiation, they keep on killing
OL,16,Ftheir own citizenry," Pahlavi said.
OL,18,F"You cannot trust such a regime. It's
OL,19,Fjust trying to buy time. This is
OL,20,Fpartly the reason why I think this
OL,21,Fdeal will not work or will not last."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781722095
OL,3,CIran-US deal ignores what Iranian
OL,4,Cpeople want, son of last Shah tells
OL,5,CITV News
OL,7,FWhilst his anger is reserved for the
OL,8,Fleaders of the country of his birth,
OL,9,Fhe appears sceptical of the agreements
OL,10,Fthat may have been achieved by those
OL,11,Fin charge of the nation in which he
OL,12,Fnow lives.
OL,14,F"Whether there is a deal or not, our
OL,15,Ffight for liberty continues," he said.
OL,17,F"Whether we are alone in this fight or
OL,18,Fnot remains to be seen. We hope that
OL,19,Fthe free world will be on our side
OL,20,Fthis time, and instead of throwing a
OL,21,Frope to this regime yet again."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
